						               													<description>Ma-Riot is a blindfolded board game themed on the magical sport of &amp;quot;Ma-Riot&amp;quot; from another world. This is Wonderland, a land in another world. This year, the popular Ma-Riot League begins again. This is the gateway to success for young mages. Players become up-and-coming mages and form teams called &amp;quot;clans&amp;quot; with stuffed animal &amp;quot;puppets&amp;quot; to compete in the Ma-Riot League.&amp;#10;The game takes place on a 5 by 5 grid, every player has their own copy of the board on which they place their puppets so the other players can't see them. You command them to guess the positions of the invisible opposing player's Puppets and attack them by unleashing spells. Sometimes, Mags' trump card, the Clan Spell, is used to change the course of the game. Players earn points by hitting other player's puppets, first player to earn the desired amount of points wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
